snippet.title: NB
snippet.description:
NotiBomba (NB) is a media company based in United States.

NB is the leading in news service that brings context and perspective to a growing millennial audience. We share the news in text, video, audio and images, and we take them to our audience wherever they are.

NotiBomba (NB) es una empresa de medios fundada en 2015 en Estados Unidos.

Compartimos las noticias en texto, video, audio e imágenes, y las llevamos a nuestra audiencia donde sea que estén.
